   "info" : "<table width=\"100%\" summary=\"page for hla\"><tr><td>hla</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\n<h2>The HLA data</h2>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>This data set contains HLA markers DRB, DQA, DQB and phenotypes\nof 271 Schizophrenia patients (y=1) and controls (y=0). Genotypes for 3 HLA\nloci have prefixes name (e.g., &quot;DQB&quot;) and a suffix for each of two alleles \n(&quot;.a1&quot; and &quot;.a2&quot;).\n</p>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<pre>data(hla)</pre>\n<h3>Format</h3>\n<p>A data frame containing 271 rows and 8 columns</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p>Dr Padraig Wright of Pfizer</p>\n",
